The type IV secretion system of Patescibacteria is homologous to the bacterial monoderm conjugation machinery
María del Mar Quiñonero-Coronel1, Pedro J. Cabello-Yeves2,3, Jose M. Haro-Moreno3, FranciscoRodriguez- Valera3 and M.
PilarGarcillán-Barcia 1,*
